Chapter 1:  Introduction.

If you are reading this book, it shows that you are interested in learning
more detailed information about tournament challenge events.  For general
information about the tournament, read the tournament/quest board or pick
up the book titled 'Tournament Leaflet".  This book is designed to give
detailed information on specific events.  This book will describe
challenge events that will take place in various arenas throughout the
known mud world.  See other books for pocket descriptions of other events
to take place in other areas of the Mud. 
